                  <p class="cs-testimonial__text">Joining DevSoc and competing in the annual hackathon in my second year changed my trajectory. The cybersecurity electives with Dr. Geldenhuys gave me a focus I didn&rsquo;t know I was looking for &mdash; now I&rsquo;m doing my Honours in digital forensics.</p>
